.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263574476/image_1263574476.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742016-axcelis-technologies-navigating-turbulence-as-ev-and-semiconductor-markets-stumble", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 15:05:47"}, {"id": "4741806", "title": "Enbridge Vs. Enterprise Products Partners: Why I'm Buying One Of These 6% Yielding Dividend Aristocrats In 2025", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Photo of ecstatic overjoyed man rained with bucks banknotes achieving success while isolated with red background\" data-id=\"1168355040\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1168355040/image_1168355040.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Deagreez</p></figcaption></figure><div cla